-- Former Olympus CEO Woodford says ready to return: report
-- 
-- Thu Nov 24, 2011 8:09pm EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/11/25/us-olympus-woodford-report-idUSTRE7AO02120111125

 

 TOKYO  (Reuters) - Former Olympus Corp CEO Michael Woodford said he is ready to return to the company but added the decision is up to shareholders, Kyodo news agency reported on Friday. 
 Woodford arrived at Olympus headquarters in Tokyo earlier on Friday in a boardroom showdown a month after he was fired and went public with suspicions about the company's past M&A deals. (Reporting by  Isabel Reynolds ; Editing by  Edwina Gibbs )